      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/01_Adiparva/07_sambhavaparva/09_pANDava-vardhanam/135_karNa-rAjya-lAbhaH/</link>
